@startuml
actor User
participant ":Parser" as P
participant ":ListArchiveCommand" as LAC
participant ":ApplicationList" as AL

User -> P : parse("list archive")
note right of P : Handled directly, no parser class
P --> LAC : create

LAC -> AL : getApplication(i) [for each]
note right of LAC
  First pass counts archived apps.
  Second pass displays them with
  a sequential display index.
end note
LAC --> User : archived applications or empty message
@enduml
